
                  geant4-00-01-ref-15
                  ===================

geant4-00-01-ref-15 is geant4-00-01-ref-14 plus:

run-V00-01-04             - Version (tag name) & date printed.
geomvol-V00-01-02         - G4TransportationManager: improved singleton
                            implementation.
photolepton_hadronV01-00-00  - Fix for warnings.
persistency-V00-01-10     - bug fix in G4PHCofThisEvent, G4PHCofThisEvent,
                            G4PersistentEventMan
PersistentEx01-V00-01-04  - Added short example of using HepODBMS tag
                            database (createTag, readTag)
                          - Bug fixes
PersistentEx02-V00-01-02  - added readDB example
                          - more bug fixes (TrackerSD)
config-V00-01-16          - architecture.gmk: set G4_HAVE_BOOL for SUN-CC5. 
                          - common.gmk: fixed minor typo in
                            G4OODDLX_SCHEMA_NAME
g3tog4-V00-01-cand03      - Candidate release version, dictionary-migrated.
config-V00-01-17          - architecture.gmk: fixes for WIN/NT.
                            o fixed path for OSPACELIBS
                            o removed -DG4NOT_ISO_DELETES flag
examples-V00-01-17        - Include PersistentEx tags above.
                          - Correct vacuum in ExN02.
